<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹dẖ rbnạ rạ̉s</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ại̹dẖ̊ rabũnā rā̊̉suⁿ
 wamil̊wủhu naḥ̊nu
 fal̊yan̊tafi ạl̊kẖaẘfu ại̹dẖaⁿạ
 wālsẖãkũ wāl̊ḥuz̊nu

[V2]
 2- qad̊ dakẖala ạlsãmā
 kasābiqiⁿ lanā
 wafī ạlsãmā ạlậna bihi
 ạảẙḍaⁿạ maqāmunā

[V3]
 3- biạlrũwḥi maq̊rūnūn̊
 birā̊̉sinā ạl̊qadīr̊
 waḥas̊ba ṣūraẗi ạlạảmīn̊
 jamīʿunā naṣīr̊

[V4]
 4- fafī ạlṭãrīqi ạlận̊
 taḥ̊faẓunā ạlnĩʿ̊mah̊
 ḥatãy̱ narāhu biạl̊ʿīān̊
 wanasẖ̊kura ạlrãḥ̊mah̊</lyrics>
